"{\"uid\": \"allure.com-story-sara-hughes-2024-olympics-beauty-routine\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Welcome toShelf Life, where Olympians are breaking down the beauty routines carrying them through the 2024 Paris Games.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 119, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"toShelf\", \"from\": 8, \"to\": 15}, {\"ngram\": \"Life\", \"from\": 16, \"to\": 20}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympians\", \"from\": 28, \"to\": 37}, {\"ngram\": \"the beauty routines\", \"from\": 56, \"to\": 75}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Paris Games\", \"from\": 98, \"to\": 118}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Today, beach volleyball player Sara Hughes reveals all the ways she's battling sweat and sand, including her favorite anti-chafe stick, the drugstore hairspray that keeps her ponytail intact, and the facial sunscreen that lasts for entire matches.\", \"from\": 120, \"to\": 367, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 156, \"end\": 162, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\", \"score\": 0.9999999999754436, \"rank\": 1.4050449404654993e-11, \"text\": \"Hughes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all the ways\", \"from\": 171, \"to\": 183}, {\"ngram\": \"sweat\", \"from\": 199, \"to\": 204}, {\"ngram\": \"sand\", \"from\": 209, \"to\": 213}, {\"ngram\": \"her favorite anti-chafe stick\", \"from\": 225, \"to\": 254}, {\"ngram\": \"the drugstore hairspray\", \"from\": 256, \"to\": 279}, {\"ngram\": \"her ponytail\", \"from\": 291, \"to\": 303}, {\"ngram\": \"the facial sunscreen\", \"from\": 316, \"to\": 336}, {\"ngram\": \"entire matches\", \"from\": 352, \"to\": 366}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You know when you go to the beach and you wind up with sand in all your nooks and crannies that feels like it'll never wash off?\", \"from\": 369, \"to\": 497, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the beach\", \"from\": 393, \"to\": 402}, {\"ngram\": \"sand\", \"from\": 424, \"to\": 428}, {\"ngram\": \"all your nooks\", \"from\": 432, \"to\": 446}, {\"ngram\": \"crannies\", \"from\": 451, \"to\": 459}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For beach volleyball athletes, that's a lifestyle.\", \"from\": 498, \"to\": 548, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"beach volleyball athletes\", \"from\": 502, \"to\": 527}, {\"ngram\": \"a lifestyle\", \"from\": 536, \"to\": 547}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Players like USA Volleyball's Sara Hughes practically live in two-piece bathing suits-and while that might seem like the result of sexualization to some, Hughes asserts that it's not as uncomfortable-or impractical-as it looks.\", \"from\": 549, \"to\": 776, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 562, \"end\": 576, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Volleyball\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"USA Volleyball\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Volleyball\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Volleyball\"}, {\"begin\": 584, \"end\": 590, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\", \"score\": 0.9999999999754436, \"rank\": 1.4050449404654993e-11, \"text\": \"Hughes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\"}, {\"begin\": 703, \"end\": 709, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\", \"score\": 0.9999999999754436, \"rank\": 1.4050449404654993e-11, \"text\": \"Hughes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Players\", \"from\": 549, \"to\": 556}, {\"ngram\": \"two-piece bathing suits\", \"from\": 611, \"to\": 634}, {\"ngram\": \"the result\", \"from\": 666, \"to\": 676}, {\"ngram\": \"sexualization\", \"from\": 680, \"to\": 693}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We get a lot of people mentioning, 'Oh, they are forcing you to be in bathing suits when you play.'\", \"from\": 778, \"to\": 878, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 786, \"to\": 791}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 795, \"to\": 801}, {\"ngram\": \"bathing suits\", \"from\": 849, \"to\": 862}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Honestly, I love playing in a bathing suit,\\\" she says.\", \"from\": 879, \"to\": 933, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a bathing suit\", \"from\": 907, \"to\": 921}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Having sand stuck in spandex or tight-fitting clothes, it's not fun.\", \"from\": 934, \"to\": 1003, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"sand\", \"from\": 942, \"to\": 946}, {\"ngram\": \"spandex\", \"from\": 956, \"to\": 963}, {\"ngram\": \"tight-fitting clothes\", \"from\": 967, \"to\": 988}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A bathing suit is a lot more freeing.\\\"\", \"from\": 1004, \"to\": 1042, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A bathing suit\", \"from\": 1004, \"to\": 1018}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot more freeing\", \"from\": 1022, \"to\": 1040}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Of course, all that sand, sweat, and sun exposure requires a very specific beauty routine-one that keeps Hughes's skin protected from sunburns and chafing, washes off the sand and sunscreen effectively, and moisturizes enough to prevent her skin from getting dry or irritated (especially around the bikini line).\", \"from\": 1044, \"to\": 1356, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1149, \"end\": 1155, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\", \"score\": 0.9999999999754436, \"rank\": 1.4050449404654993e-11, \"text\": \"Hughes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all that sand\", \"from\": 1055, \"to\": 1068}, {\"ngram\": \"sweat\", \"from\": 1070, \"to\": 1075}, {\"ngram\": \"sun exposure\", \"from\": 1081, \"to\": 1093}, {\"ngram\": \"a very specific beauty routine\", \"from\": 1103, \"to\": 1133}, {\"ngram\": \"sunburns\", \"from\": 1178, \"to\": 1186}, {\"ngram\": \"chafing\", \"from\": 1191, \"to\": 1198}, {\"ngram\": \"the sand\", \"from\": 1211, \"to\": 1219}, {\"ngram\": \"her skin\", \"from\": 1281, \"to\": 1289}, {\"ngram\": \"the bikini line\", \"from\": 1339, \"to\": 1354}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As she and her doubles partner Kelly Cheng prepared to compete at the 2024 Olympic Games in Paris, Hughes broke down the routine she's bringing to the village.\", \"from\": 1357, \"to\": 1516, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1388, \"end\": 1393, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Kapoor\", \"score\": 0.8994325190981639, \"rank\": 0.11181214684410276, \"text\": \"Kelly\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Kapoor\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Kapoor\"}, {\"begin\": 1449, \"end\": 1454, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.2750005635559988e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1456, \"end\": 1462, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\", \"score\": 0.9999999999754436, \"rank\": 1.4050449404654993e-11, \"text\": \"Hughes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1423, \"to\": 1445}, {\"ngram\": \"the routine\", \"from\": 1474, \"to\": 1485}, {\"ngram\": \"the village\", \"from\": 1504, \"to\": 1515}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I love a high ponytail.\", \"from\": 1518, \"to\": 1541, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a high ponytail\", \"from\": 1525, \"to\": 1540}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have really long hair, so I have to put three hair ties in to make sure it stays in place.\", \"from\": 1542, \"to\": 1634, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"really long hair\", \"from\": 1549, \"to\": 1565}, {\"ngram\": \"three hair ties\", \"from\": 1584, \"to\": 1599}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 1628, \"to\": 1633}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Depending on the day, I will have the ponytail in a braid so there is no hair flying around.\", \"from\": 1635, \"to\": 1727, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 1648, \"to\": 1655}, {\"ngram\": \"the ponytail\", \"from\": 1669, \"to\": 1681}, {\"ngram\": \"a braid\", \"from\": 1685, \"to\": 1692}, {\"ngram\": \"no hair\", \"from\": 1705, \"to\": 1712}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But sometimes I just let it free, and I put two tiny braids just for texture and a cute style.\", \"from\": 1728, \"to\": 1822, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"two tiny braids\", \"from\": 1772, \"to\": 1787}, {\"ngram\": \"texture\", \"from\": 1797, \"to\": 1804}, {\"ngram\": \"a cute style\", \"from\": 1809, \"to\": 1821}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If it'sreallyhot, I will just throw it up in a bun.\", \"from\": 1823, \"to\": 1874, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a bun\", \"from\": 1868, \"to\": 1873}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sometimes I will use theDae hair gel[to slick my hair back], but I also love hairspray.Tresemm\\u00e9 Extra Hold Hairsprayhas been my go-to lately because they also have a travel size.\", \"from\": 1875, \"to\": 2053, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"theDae hair\", \"from\": 1896, \"to\": 1907}, {\"ngram\": \"gel[to\", \"from\": 1908, \"to\": 1914}, {\"ngram\": \"my hair\", \"from\": 1921, \"to\": 1928}, {\"ngram\": \"hairspray\", \"from\": 1952, \"to\": 1961}, {\"ngram\": \"Tresemm\\u00e9 Extra Hold Hairsprayhas\", \"from\": 1962, \"to\": 1994}, {\"ngram\": \"my go\", \"from\": 2000, \"to\": 2005}, {\"ngram\": \"a travel size\", \"from\": 2039, \"to\": 2052}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So it fits well in my suitcaseandit really holds.\", \"from\": 2054, \"to\": 2103, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my suitcaseandit\", \"from\": 2073, \"to\": 2089}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dae Amazon Tresemm\\u00e9 Amazon K18 Amazon Hair care [between games] is so important.\", \"from\": 2105, \"to\": 2191, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Dae Amazon Tresemm\\u00e9 Amazon\", \"from\": 2105, \"to\": 2131}, {\"ngram\": \"K18 Amazon Hair\", \"from\": 2132, \"to\": 2147}, {\"ngram\": \"care\", \"from\": 2148, \"to\": 2152}, {\"ngram\": \"games\", \"from\": 2162, \"to\": 2167}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Right now, I am using the Nexxusshampooandconditioner.\", \"from\": 2192, \"to\": 2246, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Nexxusshampooandconditioner\", \"from\": 2214, \"to\": 2245}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am naturally blonde and I do not dye my hair, so I like to keep that color.\", \"from\": 2247, \"to\": 2324, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my hair\", \"from\": 2286, \"to\": 2293}, {\"ngram\": \"that color\", \"from\": 2313, \"to\": 2323}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The John Freida Sheer Blondeshampooandconditioner, I really like.\", \"from\": 2325, \"to\": 2390, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The John Freida Sheer Blondeshampooandconditioner\", \"from\": 2325, \"to\": 2374}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And then a couple of times [per week] I use theK18 hair mask.\", \"from\": 2391, \"to\": 2452, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"And then a couple\", \"from\": 2391, \"to\": 2408}, {\"ngram\": \"times\", \"from\": 2412, \"to\": 2417}, {\"ngram\": \"week\", \"from\": 2423, \"to\": 2427}, {\"ngram\": \"theK18 hair mask\", \"from\": 2435, \"to\": 2451}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Getting out of the shower, I use aWet Brushbecause I have really tangly hair.\", \"from\": 2453, \"to\": 2530, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the shower\", \"from\": 2468, \"to\": 2478}, {\"ngram\": \"aWet Brushbecause\", \"from\": 2486, \"to\": 2503}, {\"ngram\": \"really tangly hair\", \"from\": 2511, \"to\": 2529}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I used to not be as gentle when brushing my hair until I learned how bad that is.\", \"from\": 2531, \"to\": 2612, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my hair\", \"from\": 2572, \"to\": 2579}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I just start from the bottom.\", \"from\": 2613, \"to\": 2642, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the bottom\", \"from\": 2631, \"to\": 2641}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nexxus Ulta Beauty Nexxus Ulta Beauty John Frieda Target John Frieda Target I do not go to bed with my hair wet.\", \"from\": 2644, \"to\": 2764, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ulta Beauty John Frieda Target John Frieda Target\", \"from\": 2670, \"to\": 2719}, {\"ngram\": \"bed\", \"from\": 2735, \"to\": 2738}, {\"ngram\": \"my hair wet\", \"from\": 2744, \"to\": 2755}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I refuse to do that because I know that's not good for it.\", \"from\": 2765, \"to\": 2823, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So I will either make sure I have time to let it air dry before going to bed.\", \"from\": 2824, \"to\": 2901, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 2858, \"to\": 2862}, {\"ngram\": \"bed\", \"from\": 2897, \"to\": 2900}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Or if I have to, I will blow dry it a little bit.\", \"from\": 2902, \"to\": 2951, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I try not to use a lot of heat on my hair.\", \"from\": 2952, \"to\": 2994, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 2969, \"to\": 2974}, {\"ngram\": \"heat\", \"from\": 2978, \"to\": 2982}, {\"ngram\": \"my hair\", \"from\": 2986, \"to\": 2993}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But when I style it, I have been having fun with theShark hair dryerthat has all the different attachments.\", \"from\": 2995, \"to\": 3102, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fun\", \"from\": 3035, \"to\": 3038}, {\"ngram\": \"theShark hair\", \"from\": 3044, \"to\": 3057}, {\"ngram\": \"dryerthat\", \"from\": 3058, \"to\": 3067}, {\"ngram\": \"all the different attachments\", \"from\": 3072, \"to\": 3101}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wet Brush Amazon Shark Ulta Beauty For me, that pre-match routine is really important.\", \"from\": 3104, \"to\": 3194, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3115, \"end\": 3121, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_rainforest\", \"score\": 0.7485883873651825, \"rank\": 0.3358235294794502, \"text\": \"Amazon\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_rainforest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_rainforest\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that pre-match routine\", \"from\": 3147, \"to\": 3169}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have definitely been trying to simplify my skin-care routine.\", \"from\": 3195, \"to\": 3258, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my skin-care routine\", \"from\": 3237, \"to\": 3257}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the morning, all I really do is wash my face with warm water, then I useClean Skin Club towelsto dry because I have learned how bad it is to overuse your towels and wipe your face with all the bacteria on your bath towel.\", \"from\": 3259, \"to\": 3483, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the morning\", \"from\": 3262, \"to\": 3273}, {\"ngram\": \"my face\", \"from\": 3299, \"to\": 3306}, {\"ngram\": \"warm water\", \"from\": 3312, \"to\": 3322}, {\"ngram\": \"your towels\", \"from\": 3411, \"to\": 3422}, {\"ngram\": \"your face\", \"from\": 3432, \"to\": 3441}, {\"ngram\": \"all the bacteria\", \"from\": 3447, \"to\": 3463}, {\"ngram\": \"your bath towel\", \"from\": 3467, \"to\": 3482}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I put a really gentle daily lotion on because I have dry skin.\", \"from\": 3484, \"to\": 3546, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a really gentle daily lotion\", \"from\": 3490, \"to\": 3518}, {\"ngram\": \"dry skin\", \"from\": 3537, \"to\": 3545}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are out in the sun, so the number one priority as a beach volleyball player is applying my sunscreen.\", \"from\": 3548, \"to\": 3652, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the sun\", \"from\": 3562, \"to\": 3569}, {\"ngram\": \"the number one priority\", \"from\": 3574, \"to\": 3597}, {\"ngram\": \"a beach volleyball player\", \"from\": 3601, \"to\": 3626}, {\"ngram\": \"my sunscreen\", \"from\": 3639, \"to\": 3651}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lots of [volleyball players] like to wear visors when they play, but I actually hate wearing the visor, so I do not have that extra shade protection.\", \"from\": 3653, \"to\": 3802, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Lots\", \"from\": 3653, \"to\": 3657}, {\"ngram\": \"[volleyball players\", \"from\": 3661, \"to\": 3680}, {\"ngram\": \"visors\", \"from\": 3695, \"to\": 3701}, {\"ngram\": \"the visor\", \"from\": 3746, \"to\": 3755}, {\"ngram\": \"that extra shade protection\", \"from\": 3774, \"to\": 3801}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have been using theBliss Block Star Daily Mineral SPF 30for my face [Hughes is a paid partner of Bliss].\", \"from\": 3803, \"to\": 3909, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3874, \"end\": 3880, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\", \"score\": 0.9999999999754436, \"rank\": 1.4050449404654993e-11, \"text\": \"Hughes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\"}, {\"begin\": 3902, \"end\": 3907, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arthur_Bliss\", \"score\": 0.9575242579407588, \"rank\": 0.04435996446783211, \"text\": \"Bliss\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arthur_Bliss\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arthur_Bliss\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"theBliss Block Star Daily Mineral SPF 30for\", \"from\": 3821, \"to\": 3864}, {\"ngram\": \"a paid partner\", \"from\": 3884, \"to\": 3898}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have really sensitive and red skin, but that mineral sunscreen has a tint, so it gives a little bit of a makeup look.\", \"from\": 3910, \"to\": 4029, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"really sensitive and red skin\", \"from\": 3917, \"to\": 3946}, {\"ngram\": \"that mineral sunscreen\", \"from\": 3952, \"to\": 3974}, {\"ngram\": \"a tint\", \"from\": 3979, \"to\": 3985}, {\"ngram\": \"a little bit\", \"from\": 3999, \"to\": 4011}, {\"ngram\": \"a makeup look\", \"from\": 4015, \"to\": 4028}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Clean Skin Club Amazon Bliss Ulta Beauty Neutrogena Amazon My number one thing is I love using [at night is] aNeutrogena makeup removing balm.\", \"from\": 4031, \"to\": 4179, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4048, \"end\": 4054, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_rainforest\", \"score\": 0.7485883873651825, \"rank\": 0.3358235294794502, \"text\": \"Amazon\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_rainforest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_rainforest\"}, {\"begin\": 4076, \"end\": 4086, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Neutrogena\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Neutrogena\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Neutrogena\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Neutrogena\"}, {\"begin\": 4088, \"end\": 4094, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_rainforest\", \"score\": 0.7485883873651825, \"rank\": 0.3358235294794502, \"text\": \"Amazon\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_rainforest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_rainforest\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"night\", \"from\": 4130, \"to\": 4135}, {\"ngram\": \"aNeutrogena makeup\", \"from\": 4140, \"to\": 4158}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I want to make sure I get all the sunscreen off my face, all the sand off my face.\", \"from\": 4180, \"to\": 4262, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all the sunscreen\", \"from\": 4206, \"to\": 4223}, {\"ngram\": \"my face\", \"from\": 4228, \"to\": 4235}, {\"ngram\": \"my face\", \"from\": 4254, \"to\": 4261}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then I will go on with face wash. Then I use azelaic acid to help with acne and brown spots.\", \"from\": 4263, \"to\": 4355, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"face wash\", \"from\": 4286, \"to\": 4295}, {\"ngram\": \"azelaic acid\", \"from\": 4308, \"to\": 4320}, {\"ngram\": \"acne and brown spots\", \"from\": 4334, \"to\": 4354}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then I just put a moisturizer on and I am good to go.\", \"from\": 4356, \"to\": 4409, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a moisturizer\", \"from\": 4372, \"to\": 4385}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There are days when you are either having a breakout or you do not feel your best and you just want to look really good on the court.\", \"from\": 4411, \"to\": 4544, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"days\", \"from\": 4421, \"to\": 4425}, {\"ngram\": \"a breakout\", \"from\": 4453, \"to\": 4463}, {\"ngram\": \"the court\", \"from\": 4534, \"to\": 4543}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If I have extra redness or something that I want to cover, I feel comfortable in theNars Radiant Creamy Concealer.\", \"from\": 4545, \"to\": 4659, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4642, \"end\": 4648, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Creamy\", \"score\": 0.9999999939159352, \"rank\": 4.0313501473061116e-09, \"text\": \"Creamy\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q215380\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Creamy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Creamy\"}, {\"begin\": 4649, \"end\": 4658, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Concealer\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Concealer\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Concealer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Concealer\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"extra redness\", \"from\": 4555, \"to\": 4568}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 4572, \"to\": 4581}, {\"ngram\": \"theNars\", \"from\": 4626, \"to\": 4633}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sometimes I get my eyelashes lifted and tinted because then I do not have to do anything; you feel like you are wearing mascara, but you are really not.\", \"from\": 4660, \"to\": 4812, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my eyelashes\", \"from\": 4676, \"to\": 4688}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 4740, \"to\": 4748}, {\"ngram\": \"mascara\", \"from\": 4780, \"to\": 4787}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But if I do not have that done, sometimes I do put a littleCovergirl mascaraon just to feel like there is a little bit more there.\", \"from\": 4813, \"to\": 4943, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a littleCovergirl\", \"from\": 4864, \"to\": 4881}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It does great things for my lashes.\", \"from\": 4944, \"to\": 4979, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"great things\", \"from\": 4952, \"to\": 4964}, {\"ngram\": \"my lashes\", \"from\": 4969, \"to\": 4978}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I like more natural-looking lipwear, and the light pink shade ofFenty Gloss Bombis perfect for me.\", \"from\": 4980, \"to\": 5078, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more natural-looking lipwear\", \"from\": 4987, \"to\": 5015}, {\"ngram\": \"ofFenty Gloss Bombis\", \"from\": 5042, \"to\": 5062}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is so lightweight but gives me a slight color and glossy finish.\", \"from\": 5079, \"to\": 5146, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a slight color and glossy finish\", \"from\": 5113, \"to\": 5145}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nars Ulta Beauty CoverGirl Ulta Beauty Fenty Beauty Ulta Beauty Before I get in my bathing suit, I applyBliss Block Star Sheer Liquid Daily Sunscreen SPF 50everywhere on my body.\", \"from\": 5148, \"to\": 5332, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5167, \"end\": 5176, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CoverGirl\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"CoverGirl\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CoverGirl\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CoverGirl\"}, {\"begin\": 5178, \"end\": 5189, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ulta_Beauty\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ulta Beauty\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ulta_Beauty\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ulta_Beauty\"}, {\"begin\": 5191, \"end\": 5203, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fenty_Beauty\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Fenty Beauty\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fenty_Beauty\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fenty_Beauty\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my bathing suit\", \"from\": 5228, \"to\": 5243}, {\"ngram\": \"Block Star Sheer Liquid Daily Sunscreen SPF\", \"from\": 5258, \"to\": 5301}, {\"ngram\": \"my body\", \"from\": 5318, \"to\": 5325}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We usually go out and warm up an hour before we play, so I apply [in the hotel] right before we go to enter the beach.\", \"from\": 5333, \"to\": 5451, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the hotel\", \"from\": 5402, \"to\": 5411}, {\"ngram\": \"the beach\", \"from\": 5441, \"to\": 5450}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I warm up for an hour, and then the match is usually an hour, and I feel pretty covered if I do that.\", \"from\": 5452, \"to\": 5553, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an hour\", \"from\": 5466, \"to\": 5473}, {\"ngram\": \"the match\", \"from\": 5484, \"to\": 5493}, {\"ngram\": \"an hour\", \"from\": 5505, \"to\": 5512}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I know spray is really easy to use, but I stay away